Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.59,0:01:01.95,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}试着想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.71,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}自己能做到什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:09.49,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}有出乎意料的变故
