Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:36.84,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}用最美的笑容  出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:41.92,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}现在向未知的世界起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:48.24,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}未来的选择  做决定的是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:50.64,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}去追逐梦想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:52.20,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}也会有想哭的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:57.85,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}那是最重要的愿望  不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:02.72,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}一定能和明天的你再次相见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:09.97,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}get out of the gate true sky
