Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:30.20,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}どこから朝になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:32.36,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}静かな空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:35.63,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}見ないふりをした指きり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:37.86,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}小指のさき
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:41.14,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}笑われた月なら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:44.15,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}消えてゆくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:48.16,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}昨日の方角へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:51.17,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}うそつき  臆病者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:54.18,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}みんなまとめて僕なら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:22:59.82,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}咲いていたのは夢の中だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.60,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}月の影に隠してた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:05.22,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}本当はね  泣いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.43,0:23:08.04,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}涙はもう流れない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:11.08,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}かれてしまったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.19,0:23:13.84,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}何もかも許せたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.92,0:23:17.50,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}流れるかもしれないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.74,0:23:24.90,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}守りたいものばかりだな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:30.20,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}白昼从何而来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:32.36,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}静寂的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:35.63,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}装作没看见拉着钩的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:37.86,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}小指的尖端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:41.14,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}嘲笑我的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:44.15,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}已经消失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:48.16,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}迈向昨天的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:51.17,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}骗子  胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:54.18,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:22:59.82,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}只能在梦中绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.60,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}躲进月光的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:05.22,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}我真的哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.43,0:23:08.04,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}但却没法流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:11.08,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}因为我的眼泪已经枯竭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.19,0:23:13.84,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}如果能原谅一切的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.92,0:23:17.50,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}或许能再流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.74,0:23:24.90,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}因为都是我想要守护之物


